{
  "doc_id": "45149",
  "text": "Several studies have been conducted on estimating direct heritabilities for economic traits with no attention to the existence of maternal effects in native fowl [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ). But only a few estimates are available for maternal genetic and permanent environmental effects [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] . So far, no estimate is available for trends based on the best model for economic traits in these populations.",
